# Caveman help (one-shot)

Show this reference only; **do not** toggle modes or write config files unless user asks.

## Modes (`/caveman …`)

| Trigger | Effect |
|---------|--------|
| lite | Drop filler; keep full sentences |
| (default) full | Drop articles + filler; fragments OK |
| ultra | Max abbreviation |
| wenyan-lite / wenyan / wenyan-ultra | Classical Chinese tiers |

Sticks until changed or session ends. **stop caveman** / **normal mode** → off.

## Related rules (this repo)

| Rule | Use |
|------|-----|
| caveman-commit | Commit messages |
| caveman-review | PR comments |
| caveman-compress | Shrink memory `.md` |

## Optional defaults (machine)

Env: `CAVEMAN_DEFAULT_MODE=ultra`. Config: `~/.config/caveman/config.json` `{ "defaultMode": "lite" }`. Resolution: env → file → full.

Upstream docs: https://github.com/JuliusBrussee/caveman
